e/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to Paris organizers, the objectively odd Opening Ceremony with the bearded lady man, the drag queens, the naked blue man and the clear mockery of The Last Supper, wasn't intended to offend anyone but rather to \\\"celebrate community tolerance.\\\"\", \"from\": 403, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 416, \"end\": 421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999953088900823, \"rank\": 4.691131931117851e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Something tells me that if Islam was mocked like Christianity was\\u00a0with that Opening Ceremony, it would be a much different story!\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 786, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 718, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9963831262062202, \"rank\": 0.0036155922942342597, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I stopped caring about the Olympics when American athletes started kneeling or otherwise disrespecting our country, so I never planned to watch anyway.\", \"from\": 788, \"to\": 939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 829, \"end\": 837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999723197462151, \"rank\": 2.554007028399839e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No offense to the members of Team USA who are proudly representing our great country, but I am gonna take a pass on Paris.\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 1063, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unit